RumorFact.Text: The Nomai conducted a survey expedition to the exterior of Dark Bramble.

ExploreFact.Text: The Nomai found frozen species inside this glacier on the underside of Dark Bramble's north pole.
The Nomai hypothesized that these species originated within the frozen planet, and were launched within shards of ice to the planets that became their new habitats.

RumorFact.Text: A Nomai named Escall discovered this nest while trying to reach the Vessel.

ExploreFact.Text: A cluster of anglerfish eggs guarded fiercely by anglerfish deep within Dark Bramble.
A Nomai named Escall discovered this nest on a desperate mission to reach the Vessel. He.. met a gruesome end.
Escall noted that the eggs were warm, gelatinous, and filled with liquid.
